            <scopecontent>
                <p>This volume records transactions at an unidentified tavern in Philadelphia. The
                    daily accounts list purchases and receipts for liquor and food sales, and
                    miscellaneous charges, such as "segars" (cigars) and entrance fees. Each
                    month's accounts are recapitulated and totaled.</p>
            </scopecontent>


